Other tasks to complete,

  1)  Download the sendgrid api library from <a href="https://sendgrid-open-source.s3.amazonaws.com/sendgrid-php/sendgrid-php.zip" >here</a>
  2)  Require the library from downloaded package:

  require_once('path/to/sendgrid-php/sendgrid-php.php');

  3)  Setup basic configuration settings including:
        Your sendgrid API kay: email_sendgrid_api_key
        Default template: email_sendgrid_template
        Mail footer : email_footer
        Sending address: email_from_address
        Sending Name: email_from_name
